# ESG SCORING LOGIC

Simple weighted scoring.

| Category                    | Weight |
| --------------------------- | ------ |
| Energy Efficiency           | 30%    |
| Renewable Adoption          | 25%    |
| Supply Chain Sustainability | 20%    |
| Governance Readiness        | 15%    |
| Reporting Transparency      | 10%    |

---

# SIMPLE SCORING FORMULA

```text id="2xlytw"
ESG Score =
(Energy × 0.3)
+ (Renewables × 0.25)
+ (Supply Chain × 0.2)
+ (Governance × 0.15)
+ (Transparency × 0.1)
```

Keep it simple.
Judges care about clarity, not accuracy.

